            <div class="single-post indienova-single-post fr-view">
                <p>本周，PAX 的余温尚在，但是大批游戏已经开始冲了上来，而且确实有一些明显品质还不错的独立游戏。胖布丁的《迷失岛 3》将在本周发行，《无间冥寺》、《<a href="https://indienova.com/indie-game-news/indie-express-the-longing/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">The Longing</a>》也将在本周登场。而且本周新游戏涵盖类型也较宽泛，相信必有一款适合您。</p><h4>Builders of Egypt: Prologue</h4><p>关键字：免费、城市营造、模拟、即时战略</p><p>发行日期：2020/03/02（<strong>中文支持</strong>）EA</p><p>Builders Of Egypt: Prologue 是一款讲述发生在尼罗河流域的城市建设经济战略游戏。 沉浸在一个充满金字塔的世界里，在那里你将成为古代世界的一部分。</p><p>游戏最重要的方面是通过塑造街道网格、布置建筑物及其相互关系，对城市规划进行巧妙的管理。精心设计的城市将大大提高经济效益，并可转化为城市收入。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/pic-Egypt9999OM.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3004876_MvHaSV.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3004876_lQvTam.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3004876_uVZgmr.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/1207590/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>迷失岛 3：宇宙的尘埃</h4><p>关键字：策略、冒险、解谜</p><p>发行日期：2020/03/03（<strong>中文支持</strong>）</p><p>本作是由《南瓜先生大冒险》《迷失岛》《小三角大英雄》的制作团队胖布丁打造的迷失岛系列解谜游戏续作《迷失岛 3：宇宙的尘埃》，继续带领玩家去探索这座神秘小岛所蕴含的宇宙故事。</p><p>在《迷失岛 2 时间的灰烬》结尾，小火箭终于飞向了太空。</p><p>那之后发生了什么呢？</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/02/img-2864986_TI3i91.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/02/img-2864986_C83rHt.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/02/img-2864986_gdr6Dn.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/1249010/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>Hypergalactic Psychic Table Tennis 3000</h4><p>关键字：动作、欢乐、街机</p><p>发行日期：2020/03/03（暂无中文）</p><p>一款终极（无所不用其极）的经典网球游戏 PONG 大变种。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/pic-Paddle25635J.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3011838_itg7QL.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3011838_wXXGbw.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3011838_JLRXy4.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/1233690/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>Amoeba Battle: Microscopic RTS Action</h4><p>关键字：即时战略、在线合作、卡通化</p><p>发行日期：2020/03/03（暂无中文）</p><p>一只变形虫如何击败一千只变形虫？</p><p>控制唯一幸存的一只变形虫，指导其完成变形虫最擅长的工作：进食，以获取更多力量，将您的单细胞幸存者变成阿米巴变形虫军队，夺回微观世界控制权！</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/pic-amoeba3033DT.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3025348_mIk5pc.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3025348_EYiZft.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3025348_vObjrc.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/730860/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>INFILTRIA</h4><p>关键字：Rogue-lite，战术角色扮演</p><p>发行日期：2020/03/03（暂无中文）EA</p><p>跳票到这里。</p><p>INFiLTRIA 是一款 rogue-lite RPG 生存射击游戏。游戏中的关卡由程序生成，但是角色进化会保持下来。</p><p>故事背景是有组织的恐怖分子占领了欧洲的大量地点，玩家要做的就是不惜生命代价，在恐怖分子的进攻计划被大众知道之前，歼灭他们。</p><p>尽管是常见的战术角色扮演游戏，但是程序生成地图不免让它多了一些吸引力。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/09/pic-INFILTRIA1629GY.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/09/pic-ss_f09b203e82f0fc234bfff1e7d284c21424c4cd51.1920x10801534sv.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/09/pic-ss_29787cab16ce7c5457ce25d4fc4762f98d75d258.1920x1080153908.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/950490/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>Curse of the Dead Gods（无间冥寺）</h4><p>关键字：Roguelike、黑暗奇幻、动作</p><p>发行日期：2020/03/04（<strong>中文支持</strong>）EA</p><p>一款技巧性的 Roguelike 游戏，让你探索无情而黑暗的庙宇，穿梭于无尽的密室与通道中。</p><p>你探求数不胜数的财富、追寻永生、追求神力——所有的一切都指向了这座被诅咒的神庙。这个似乎无穷无尽的深渊迷宫，充斥着致命的陷阱和怪兽。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/02/gif-Curse_dsIj6yRz.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/02/img-2729516_B19wAf.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/02/img-2729516_rP3QRY.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/1123770/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>Weakless</h4><p>关键字：冒险、唯美、解谜</p><p>发行日期：2020/03/04（<strong>中文支持</strong>）</p><p><em>Weakless</em> 是一款画风优美的解谜冒险游戏，故事发生在一个充满奇异生物与幽光的幻想世界。玩家将扮演两个被称为 Weaveling 的天真无邪的树精。他们一个目盲，一个失聪。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/pic-23239Gs.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/pic-33244I5.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3005527_nXqBmF.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3005527_ytBN8m.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3005527_HmoSCm.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/1072620/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>Deathbloom: Chapter 2</h4><p>关键字：解谜、悬疑、生存恐怖</p><p>发行日期：2020/03/04（暂无中文）</p><p>一款受到经典生存恐怖的启发而制作的游戏。</p><p>巴赫曼庄园（Bachman Manor）遍布迷宫般的走廊、卧室、门厅等。这里到处都是谜题、陷阱和隐藏的通道，这些通道将会带领玩家通往探索其黑暗历史和居住者的秘密之路。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/pic-Deathbloom3531OC.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3024999_bP3MUL.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3024999_I4Bvi9.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3024999_rEO3xB.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/1185470/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>Puddle Knights</h4><p>关键字：解谜、策略</p><p>发行日期：2020/03/04（暂无中文）</p><p>这是一款基于泥巴的益智游戏，还是有一些新意的。您可以使用骑士的披风掩盖水坑，并帮助上层阶级的人们远离卫生条件差的街道。</p><p>在这个轻松愉快的中世纪益智解谜游戏中，解决越来越棘手的难题吧！</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/pic-Puddle-13912eG.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3025248_peigeK.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3025248_98mSPM.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3025248_U0sp0k.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/1180540/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>Nocturne: Prelude</h4><p>关键字：免费、音乐、角色扮演、冒险</p><p>发行日期：2020/03/04（暂无中文）</p><p>在这款节奏游戏中，来世现在是数字化的。</p><p>在具有独特节奏战斗的跨类型 RPG 的第一章中，发现永生其实是伴随着牺牲。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/pic-Nocturne4365xS.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3025854_QmGFC8.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3025854_vluOMF.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3025854_Z9bEtG.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/883590/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>Infini</h4><p>关键字：解谜、冒险</p><p>发行日期：2020/03/04（暂无中文）</p><p>在神奇的迷幻旅程中与时间，诗歌，记忆，技术，战争和死亡进行有意义的相遇，挑战你的思维。</p><p>随着希望深入到无限中，现实世界开始因他的缺席而饱受煎熬。在这里似乎没有任何出路，而希望自然注定要继续下去。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/pic-infini4901Xl.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3026113_BKiZoK.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3026113_vO5TJ0.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3026113_17eRo8.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/1120420/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>Mystic Pillars: A Story-Based Puzzle Game（秘境之柱）</h4><p>关键字：唯美、解谜、休闲</p><p>发行日期：2020/03/05（<strong>中文支持</strong>）</p><p>秘境之柱是一款特别的冒险游戏，它拥有丰富的故事情节和出色的解谜体验，为玩家提供一场独一无二的印度文化之旅。</p><p>您将扮演一位神秘旅行者，在环游世界的旅途中邂逅了赞匹王国，解开沉睡已久的王国之谜。</p><p>随着旅途的深入，故事逐步揭开赞匹王国逐渐没落并最终沉沦的点点滴滴，真相浮出水面，情节扣人心弦。随着游戏剧情的精彩展开，谜题同样渐入佳境！</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/pic-Pillars5469BK.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3026413_AkAIPo.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3026413_501kqD.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3026413_VV8jAp.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/1197030/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>Deep Space Banana</h4><p>关键字：免费、策略、城市营造、玩家对战</p><p>发行日期：2020/03/05（暂无中文）</p><p>让您的猿猴舰队完成征服太空的任务！</p><p>在这款策略游戏中测试您作为太空征服者的防御技能。扩展您的空间站并执行令人兴奋的任务。现在就开始吧！</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/pic-bananna6082yx.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3026526_7NUQpD.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3026526_a6QTbM.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3026526_mKOkWW.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/866170/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>Wunderling</h4><p>关键字：动作、冒险、平台解谜</p><p>发行日期：2020/03/05（暂无中文）</p><p>一款复古的动作游戏，你要扮演 Wunderling，游戏的 Boss，目标是对付英雄。你最近刚刚解锁了跳跃技能。</p><p>玩家的角色停不下来，也不能改变方向，所以需要谨慎考虑……</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/pic-Wunderling-1739041.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/pic-Wunderling-27397ns.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/pic-Wunderling-37401oy.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/pic-Wunderling-47407JJ.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/732930/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>下半部分</h4><p>下半部分明日准时送上，不见不散！</p><div class="text-center"><iframe frameborder="no" border="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" width="290" height="450" src="https://indienova.com/widget/indie-game-news/guide20-0302-0308-part-2/"></iframe></div>
